Properties.PreHtml: Which support services are needed to make this event successful?
Properties.PostHtml:
Notes:
  • Audio Visual might include on-site technician, training , or TV Carts.
  • Communications might include promo or story videos, graphics (logos or other).
  • Event Support might include all support levels
  • Facilities might include special setup requests.
  • IT might include Checkin or use of a portable computer or tablet.
  • Website Promotion/Event Registration might include public or private registration and any website promotion.
  • Registered Childcare might include all childcare needs other than Sunday service times.
